## 👉 Just Want to Use Mine?

Don't want to set up your own copy? You're welcome to just use the version that's
already live and configured:

🔗 **https://riguma.github.io/asjdkacbzjch_os/**

A few things to know if you go this route:
- It's the exact same app — no sign-up, no install, just open the link.
- Your data still only lives in *your* browser, on *your* device. I (the owner of
  this repo) can't see your tasks, mood entries, money logs, or anything else you
  enter — none of that gets sent to me.
- If you want GitHub/Google Calendar sync, you'll still need your *own* GitHub
  token and your *own* Google OAuth Client ID (see the setup sections above) — my
  setup only covers hosting the app itself, not your personal sync credentials.
- Since I control this repo, I can update/change the app at any time. If you want
  full control over your own permanent copy instead, follow the "Getting Started"
  steps above to host your own.
